tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE fashion_collaborations (
    collaboration_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    celebrity_id UUID,
    designer_id UUID,
    collaboration_date DATE,
    collaboration_details TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE collaboration (
    collaboration_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    celebrity_id INT NOT NULL,
    designer_id INT NOT NULL,
    collaboration_date DATE NOT NULL,
    FOREIGN KEY (celebrity_id) REFERENCES celebrity(celebrity_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (designer_id) REFERENCES designer(designer_id)
);

CREATE TABLE fashion_collaborations (
  collaboration_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  celebrity_name VARCHAR(255),
  designer_name VARCHAR(255),
  collaboration_type VARCHAR(50),
  collaboration_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE celebrity (
  celebrity_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  celebrity_name VARCHAR(255),
  profession VARCHAR(100),
  age INT,
  nationality VARCHAR(100)
);

CREATE TABLE designer (
  designer_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  designer_name VARCHAR(255),
  brand_name VARCHAR(100),
  founded_year INT,
  country VARCHAR(100)
);

CREATE TABLE collaboration_details (
  collaboration_id INT,
  celebrity_id INT,
  designer_id INT,
  PRIMARY KEY (collaboration_id, celebrity_id, designer_id),
  FOREIGN KEY (collaboration_id) REFERENCES fashion_collaborations(collaboration_id),
  FOREIGN KEY (celebrity_id) REFERENCES celebrity(celebrity_id),
  FOREIGN KEY (designer_id) REFERENCES designer(designer_id)
);
